  </table>
  <h4>
   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml"><a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Reference/Drawing/Colour_And_Alpha/Colour_And_Alpha.htm">
 Colour
</a></code></pre>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">col = make_colour_rgb(100, 145, 255);
</code></pre>
  The above code uses the function to create a colour and store its value in the variable "col" for later use.
